data.description: This immaculate Florida home offers a quiet retreat mere minutes from major grocery, shopping, restaurants and medical. Just three minutes from Lehigh Acres Park with community pool, tennis courts, baseball/softball, picnic pavilions and more! This three bedroom, two bathroom home features a desirable split layout complete with formal living and dining areas. Enjoy the ease of cleaning tile and vinyl plank flooring - no carpet in this home! The spacious kitchen offers plenty of storage, convenient prep island, stainless steel appliances, solid surface counters, pantry, breakfast nook, and a bar overlooking the family room. Both guest bedrooms and bathroom can be closed off with a pocket door for additional privacy - an ideal layout for AirBnB and other possibilities! Lots of recent updates, including fresh interior paint, NEW 2023 Roof, NEW water softener, NEW reverse osmosis for clean drinking water, NEW stainless steel stove, 2022 AC, 2019 water heater. The primary suite features a walk-in closet and en-suite bathroom with brand new vinyl plank flooring and a new dual vanity with granite counters. Three sets of sliding doors open wide onto the spacious rear screened porch, allowing for fabulous indoor-outdoor living and entertaining! The tiki bar is included in the sale. Furniture package is available separately. You'll appreciate the roomy two car garage, the corner lot with avocado & mango trees, and charming palm trees too! Don't delay - call to schedule a tour of your new home today!
